name: Freddie Mercury
description:
Freddie Mercury:

i like the whole world to listen to my music level i want anybody in everybody to come and listen to me and look at me when i am playing. in the end i just do things very generally or whatever i feel .
the main music is not channeled into any category i want everybody to listen to it i dont write music for just japanese or just the german so it is for everybody music is limitless and sometimes when they get too close i think they seem to destroy me i dont know maybe it is my nature whatever and when they get too close they seem to tread all over me and when i lay mysel bare just seems to be my downfall maybe it is my nature maybe . maybe that is my role in life i live life to the for a while every day is passing for me ...
